OL,7,FMembers of a Glasgow paedophile gang
OL,8,Fthat plunged to "the depths of human
OL,9,Fdepravity" have been jailed for terms
OL,10,Franging from eight to 20 years for
OL,11,Ftheir part in a "monstrous" child sex
OL,12,Fabuse ring.
OL,14,FThe seven gang members will all be
OL,15,Fmonitored for life after being
OL,16,Fconvicted of gang raping a child and
OL,17,Fabusing other children in a drugs den
OL,18,Fwhere heroin and crack cocaine were
OL,19,Fused.
