OL,7,FIain Owens, 46; Elaine Lannery, 40;
OL,8,FLesley Williams, 43; Paul Brannan, 42;
OL,9,FScott Forbes, 51; Barry Watson, 48;
OL,10,Fand John Clark, 48, were convicted in
OL,11,FNovember 2023 following a trial at the
OL,12,FHigh Court in Glasgow.
OL,14,FFour members of the group, Owens,
OL,15,FLannery, Brannan and Wiilliams, were
OL,16,Falso found guilty of attempting to
OL,17,Fmurder a child.
